data.value:
1. Ensure Connect UART cable to RS 232 MAINT connector to test fixture & Ensure the P3 Jumper toggle switch position to "Short".
2. Open the command prompt and type "cd" space & paste the programming path as "C:\USERS\MMB\software\spraai4a(i)\exe" then Enter.
3. Press TAB key on the keyboard until "DVFlasher_1_10.exe" is appear on the screen then Type -enor and press Enter Key & wait until flash is erase successfully.
4. Verify the captured command prompt Screenshot with left side reference image.
